'''''Shuga''''', izwi kandi ku izina rya '''''MTV Shuga'''''<ref>MTV SHUGA PREMIERES – The BB Buzz</ref>, ni urukurikirane rw'ikinamico rwa televiziyo rwatangajwe bwa mbere mu Gushyingo 2009 kuri MTV Base mu rwego rwo kwitwa "MTV staying alive Ignite!"<ref>'MTV Shuga' has made a real difference in the fight against HIV <nowiki>https://www.fastcompany.com</nowiki> › mtvs-revolutionary-africa...</ref> . Ibice byayo bibiri byambere byahawe inshingano na MTV Networks Africa ifatanije na MTV Staying Alive Foundation<ref>Every Woman Every Child partners with the MTV Staying Alive ... <nowiki>https://www.everywomaneverychild.org</nowiki> › every-woman-e...</ref>, PEPFAR, Ubufatanye bw’umuryango urwanya virusi itera SIDA (HFG) na Guverinoma ya [[Kenya]], mu rwego rwo gukwirakwiza ubutumwa bugamije gukwirakwiza ubutumwa ku myitwarire yimibonano mpuzabitsina no kwihangana<ref>MTV Shuga: Changing social norms and behaviors with ... <nowiki>https://www.povertyactionlab.org</nowiki> › evaluation › mtv-shug...</ref>

Iyi filime yaje gukundwa cyane kandi yerekanwa mu bihugu 40 bitandukanye bya Afurika mbere yuko isohoka ku rwego mpuzamahanga kuri televiziyo zirenga 70<ref>MTV Shuga - A Multi-platform Communication Initiative ... <nowiki>https://www.comminit.com</nowiki> › content › mtv-shuga-multi...</ref>.  Ikinamico yatekerezaga ko ari urukurikirane ruvuguruzanya cyane nabasekuruza bakuru ba Kenya kuko rwarimo amashusho amwe yarimo ibintu byerekeranye n'igitsina<ref>Please Wait... | Cloudflare (togetherforgirls.org)</ref>.  Yabonye igihembo cya Zahabu muri Gicurasi 2010 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ry’itangazamakuru ryabereye i Hamburg mu [[Budage]] mu cyiciro cy’ubuzima rusange  kubera kwibanda ku rukundo, amarangamutima, n’imyitwarire y’imibonano mpuzabitsina mu rubyiruko rwo muri [[Kenya]]<ref>Shuga Season 3 is here - Mkenya Ujerumani <nowiki>https://mkenyaujerumani.de</nowiki> › 2013/12/10 › shuga-seas...</ref>. 

== MTV Shuga (2020) ==
Kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus, Shuga yagiye mu gitaramo gito cya nijoro cyiswe MTV Shuga Alone Together kigaragaza ibibazo bya Coronavirus ku ya 20 Mata 2020<ref>MTV Shuga: Alone Together | The COVID-19 Communication ... <nowiki>https://www.comminit.com</nowiki> › covid › content › mtv-shu...</ref>. Iki gitaramo cyagombaga gutambuka amajoro 65 kandi abayishyigikiye barimo [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|Umuryango w’abibumbye]] <ref>A Spoonful of Shuga: Life and love among young people in ... <nowiki>https://www.unicef.org</nowiki> › esa › documents › spoonful-s...</ref>.  Urukurikirane rushingiye muri [[Nijeriya]], [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo, [[Kenya]] na [[Kote Divuwari|Côte D'Ivoire]] kandi inkuru isobanurwa n'ibiganiro kumurongo hagati yabantu nyamukuru<ref>MTV Shuga | UN News <nowiki>https://news.un.org</nowiki> › tags › mtv-shuga</ref>. Inyandiko yanditswe na Tunde Aladese <ref name="writer" /> na Nkiru Njoku .  Nibo banditsi bakuru kuri iki gitaramo kandi banayoboye ibice. Gufata amashusho, kumurika no kwisiga byakozwe nabakinnyi ubwabo<ref>Mohale Motaung on Shooting MTV's Shuga ... - Mbare Times <nowiki>https://mbaretimes.com</nowiki> › mtvshugaalonetogether</ref>.
